  <div class="module  home-full-width-feature      has-media              has-content      ">
    
      
        <div class="module-header home-full-width-header">
          <h2 class="module-title home-full-width-module-title" style="
          
           	color:#F7AC64;
                                                                     
  		  
             margin-top:px;
          
            ">How do Sundots work?
          </h2>
        </div>
      

      
        <div class="module-body home-full-width-body">
          
            <div class="module-content home-full-width-content home-full-width-body-item">
              Sundots use 240mg of polypodium leucotomos, a fern extract backed by 30+ years of sun protection science conducted at top research institutions around the world, including Harvard Medical School. 
<br><br>
While Sundots aren't a substitute for sunscreen, the evidence is clear from over a dozen human studies and decades of use: When taken like a vitamin, this fern can help your body resist the harmful effects of the sun.
            </div>
          

          
            <div class="module-cta home-full-width-cta home-full-width-body-item">
